text: Philippa Smyth (born 9 September 1995) is an Australian rules footballer who played for the Greater Western Sydney Giants in the AFL Women's competition (AFLW). Monahan was drafted by the Giants with their fifth selection and the 73rd pick overall in the 2017 AFL Women's draft. She made her debut in a draw with at Blacktown ISP Oval in round 4 of the 2018 season.
